<h1 id="07-termbin">07. <a href="http://termbin.com/">Termbin</a></h1>
<p>This is a show of the ball, it runs via the command <code class="highlighter-rouge">nc</code> (needs to have <a href="http://nc110.sourceforge.net/">netcat</a> installed) and the insertion is very simple, example:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span class="nb">cat </span>mycode.sh | nc termbin.com 9999</code></pre></figure>

<hr />

<h1 id="08-instacode">08. <a href="http://instaco.de/">InstaCode</a></h1>
<p>This is loko, sharing is via image and you can create Wallpaper and edit your image: rotate, blur, colorschemes and among other options! Worth the click.
<img src="/assets/img/code/instacode.png" alt="InstaCode" /></p>

